[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m considering a potential feature for semi-automatic derivation of case objects and enums. It looks like Circe's generic support covers sealed traits with case objects, but right now, we only have sealed traits with case classes. I think adding a test for an ADT that includes both singleton case objects and nested sealed abstracts could be useful. I also want to explore deriving key encoders and decoders for value classes and case classes, so I'll need to search for the right APIs online.
